CreateFunctionStmt(name_path=templated_udf, return_type=STRUCT<>, argument_name_list=[x, p], signature=(ANY TYPE x, FUNCTION<INT64->BOOL> p) -> ANY TYPE, language="SQL", code="p(x)")
==

